# Page Template: Detail

## Structure

```
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Back link + Breadcrumb          │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Title + Status Badge            │
│ Metadata (date, type, location) │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Description (Markdown)          │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Action Section (form, CTA)      │
└─────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Requirements

- Server Component with `force-dynamic`
- Dynamic metadata (`generateMetadata`) for OG tags
- 404 handling (`notFound()`)
- Responsive two-column on desktop, stacked on mobile
- Action section: forms are Client Components
